    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo Out Now!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy experimenting with 70+ cards and 20+ passive items in the demo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add Beans of Production to your Wishlist and be the first to know about updates and official releases.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hone your barista skills to smash daily goals and stave off the thirsty masses in this rogue-lite match-3 deckbuilder. Play your cards right to clear ingredients, beat increasingly demanding quotas, unlock passives, and make it through the work week.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/36eb4b44308da095f1b63d1bbf371b45.poster.avif?t=1738705261\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/36eb4b44308da095f1b63d1bbf371b45.webm?t=1738705261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/24a72db813e09315d0687425586cf4fd.poster.avif?t=1738705261\" width=620 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/24a72db813e09315d0687425586cf4fd.webm?t=1738705261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/24a72db813e09315d0687425586cf4fd.mp4?t=1738705261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new cards as you make your way home each night and build an optimized deck. Choose your build: become a gourmet ingredient specialist, maximize your flexibility to think on your feet, or leverage the chaos of burning ingredients. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/0de9b966784f822db2ea82b9b8a9063b.poster.avif?t=1738705261\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/0de9b966784f822db2ea82b9b8a9063b.webm?t=1738705261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/df6887de9691658de93a0cf6aed69ea4.poster.avif?t=1738705261\" width=620 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/df6887de9691658de93a0cf6aed69ea4.webm?t=1738705261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/df6887de9691658de93a0cf6aed69ea4.mp4?t=1738705261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your match grid and unlock metaprogression features. Enhance your favorite builds or gain all-round advantages to defy the odds and beat your daily quotas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/78598ded2eb3e7aac3fa41105f1b03f2.poster.avif?t=1738705261\" width=620 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136860/extras/78598ded2eb3e7aac3fa41105f1b03f2.webm?t=1738705261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https